snippet.textDisplay:
Okay hear me out.
I usually only watch the 73 questions cause of the attractive female celebrities. However, when I watch them, I’m really only focusing on them and how pretty they are or whatever, and not on their actual answers because they are usually so shallow and just general. Then I saw this one came out, and I was like, oh, Camila is my top favorite. At least I can watch it and enjoy the scenery right? But this one felt different. Maybe I’m biased, but most of the 73 Questions just feel scripted. Like they aren’t even thinking about what answer they’re giving. But in this one, you can tell that it was an actual interview. Obviously, she knew they were coming, but her answers were just so genuine and heartfelt.
Also, her hair was gorgeous.
